  Header always set Access-Control-Allow-Origin "*"
</Location>
RedirectPermanent /.well-known/matrix/server https://matrix.altgo.us/.well-known/matrix/server
RedirectPermanent /.well-known/matrix/client https://matrix.altgo.us/.well-known/matrix/client
RedirectPermanent /.well-known/matrix/support https://matrix.altgo.us/.well-known/matrix/support
